{"tid":47620,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"關於Fb Like 抽獎既法律問題 有無讀law巴打 (1)","createTime":"2016-12-20T12:48:15.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-25T01:54:56.000Z","uid":16789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4dead3767a5208e65153824c4b764730eb68cd9c","tid":47620,"uid":16789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T12:48:15.000Z","msg":"如題 ,好多Facebook 專頁搞d Like/Like+Share就可以參加抽獎以作推銷 , 例如話我記得Apple都好似有做過 like+留言想要咩色iphone7 咁樣抽獎 (好似咁上下) 或者足球毒料都會有呢d share就抽ipad/iphone咁樣 <br />\n<br />\n但係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 根據《推廣生意的競賽牌照》發牌指引，《賭博條例》第一百四十八章第二條，推廣生意的競賽是指為推廣生意、業務或產品銷售，而籌辦、經營或管理經抽籤或碰機會而分發或分配獎品的競賽或其他計劃，須由影視處處長簽發牌照才可舉辦。至於影視處發牌時會考慮活動必須符合公眾利益、不得成為業務的核心部分，及不得提供另類賭博等，獲得發牌者須遵守一定的發牌條件<br />\n<br />\nOK,咁問題來黎啦 當時APPLE/足球毒料/其他專頁有無先拎牌照先做呢件事?  如果無既話  , 其實係咪已經犯緊法 ? <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20120209/00176_017.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20120209%2F00176_017.html&d=TYHs%2BogJ1L0HDOT4jOIEBUsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=d96f42b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20120209/00176_017.html</a><br />\n<br />\n而呢一單Case  現代教育發言人回應時指，今次活動已是第二屆舉行，之前已諮詢法律意見，指由於參加者須回答問題，並非純粹的抽獎活動，故毋須申領有關牌照，迄今為止，亦未收到政府部門跟進。<br />\n<br />\n即係話開條問題出黎 , 之後先叫人答 , 然後再簡岩既答案(自訂) 咁樣就無順要申領有關牌照, 係變左一個答中問題而唔係抽籤得獎既形式?咁樣又有無觸犯到其他任何香港既法例? 另外想問下有無人知呢件事最後點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔該哂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  純學術討論 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f571143fe6c4ebd3c6d4cb0b630c53b553ffbdac","tid":47620,"uid":16789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T12:52:39.000Z","msg":"1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c40582a77a16d95f6c5b73f9851d060b1d3b407","tid":47620,"uid":52477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T12:53:15.000Z","msg":"真係Apple做架咩 唔係Parallel Retailer黎架咩"},{"pid":"2ca66687ac4df493d2659eade7c622854b7916c7","tid":47620,"uid":16789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T12:56:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係Apple做架咩 唔係Parallel Retailer黎架咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以我都唔肯定 , 不過我記得有個page抽iphone7推到好多like"},{"pid":"90fcad968c61f2c1af8416e065dfd07e6d9f13cf","tid":47620,"uid":52477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T12:57:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>真係Apple做架咩 唔係Parallel Retailer黎架咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以我都唔肯定 , 不過我記得有個page抽iphone7推到好多like</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點會係Apple自己做呢啲dirty work"},{"pid":"6e52b8e2a52f5c3142d7d9900b2dd9019fc862cf","tid":47620,"uid":16789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T13:00:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>真係Apple做架咩 唔係Parallel Retailer黎架咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以我都唔肯定 , 不過我記得有個page抽iphone7推到好多like</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點會係Apple自己做呢啲dirty work</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我有印象姐 , 不過有無讀law既巴打可以解答到小弟既問題"},{"pid":"cf47772e508ea5d7738e440c72f29a56a22a4c4c","tid":47620,"uid":44323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T13:04:35.000Z","msg":"自己查下咩叫生意、業務或產品銷售"},{"pid":"2c70c9dc3c543727313c501755bddfce751aa566","tid":47620,"uid":16789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T13:09:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己查下咩叫生意、業務或產品銷售</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n已經全部知道哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab99efb478af435