 />\n牌照事務處 」"},{"pid":"b75f9f6a6c792eab2b03956dd855de012f7b9e8e","tid":47620,"uid":16789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T15:02:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>只要洩及機會率，唔係人人都有獎既話，就要攞牌 <br />\n<br />\n之前查詢過：<br />\n<br />\n「根據香港《賭博條例》(第148章)的定義，&quot;推廣生意的競賽&quot;是指採用抽籤 / 踫機會方式分發 / 分配獎品的遊戲，為推廣生意 / 業務 / 銷售任何產品而舉辦的競賽或計劃。任何人舉辦這些活動，必須先向本處申請牌照。而以參加次序決定得獎者的活動(如:第5名，第10名，第15 名等的參加者為得獎者)涉及碰機會，同樣需要申領推廣生意的競賽牌照。 <br />\n<br />\n民政事務總署 <br />\n牌照事務處 」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nOK,咁如果係人人都有獎 , 而同時又有大獎細獎咁樣又點計法 又洗唔洗拎牌照"},{"pid":"23e71a9da46c4e9f9f27b5369f4cfc03a529b892","tid":47620,"uid":16789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T15:31:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91049e6e937f1d79372ccd86263e10bb3c7e72a6","tid":47620,"uid":16789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T16:19:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9141c5cee960f3ddb9d2b06361f2aa7c9acc8eec","tid":47620,"uid":23137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T16:40:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}